{"title":"敦煌吟咏廿四行","authors":["张虎"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":6,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"敦煌吟咏廿四行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张虎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宏篇巨著百科书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敦煌艺术莫高窟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三危揽胜惊世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁线晕染笔奇出。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祁连雪水润杨柳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凿破混沌天地炉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏羲女娲悬日月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游龙羽人九色鹿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反弹琵琶伎乐天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羌笛羯鼓动肺腑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张骞跋涉出西域，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百国千城丝绸路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中西合璧映人生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩丹青五百窟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叹我墨迹失八九"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注），"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毁我妍鲜指可数。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北魏神笔戳人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伫立壁前觉羞辱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花落春去还复来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文物遗落谁能补？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿西部大文化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边陲明珠昭千古。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天衣飞动落彩霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁瓜州万象苏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：指墨写的经卷。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}